parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the serpentine belt can cause the loss of power steering, overheating, and damage to other engine components, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The serpentine belt detaches or breaks
causing the power steering to fail
the alternator to overheat
and the engine to stall or overheat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails
causing the vehicle to lose power and potentially leading to overheating
oil burning
or other damage to engine components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Radiator fan failure can cause the engine to overheat, leading to damage to engine components and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The radiator fan fails to operate
causing the engine to overheat and potentially leading to damage to engine components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or become inoperable, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission makes a grinding or clunking noise
the transmission fluid leaks
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the serpentine belt can cause the vehicle to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure.
symptoms: The serpentine belt becomes detached from the vehicle
the vehicle overheats
the engine stalls or loses power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake-shift interlock can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle moves without the brake pedal being pressed
the vehicle shifts into gear without the brake pedal being pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt unlatches while driving
the seat belt fails to restrain the occupant in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of a crash, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning light stays on
airbag does not deploy in a crash
horn and cruise control malfunction
clock spring failure
SRS light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the airbag warning light to stay on, rendering the airbag system inoperable, and potentially leading to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light stays on
horn and cruise control malfunction
clock spring failure
SRS light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag System Malfunction due to Recall Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to include certain vehicles in the recall, despite exhibiting symptoms of the defect, can lead to a malfunction of the airbag system, potentially resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning light stays on
airbag does not deploy in a crash
horn and cruise control malfunction
clock spring failure
SRS light appears on the dashboard.
